|Entailments={{Entailment
|Entailment.Target entailment=If government sucessfully performs action, people will flourish
|Entailment.Source inference=If shepherd successfully performs actions, sheep will flourish
}}{{Entailment
|Entailment.Target entailment=government makes decisions, people do what government wants them to
|Entailment.Source inference=shepherd makes decsions; sheep do what shepherd wants them to
}}{{Entailment
|Entailment.Target entailment=Governed people are not capable of making decisions or protecting themselves
|Entailment.Source inference=Sheep are not capable of flourishing on their own (without shepherd).
}}
